{"tid":2241214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"擾秩序案 警直認夾證供  同意「×你老母」罵警不犯法","createTime":"2020-10-13T07:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:37:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98d9a6ede5c0a5715462b4018b58bea3852de913","tid":2241214,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:12:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201013/K3CF4DXSARC67GJY6D5X7UXCUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201013%2FK3CF4DXSARC67GJY6D5X7UXCUE%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=c7489db2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201013%2FK3CF4DXSARC67GJY6D5X7UXCUE%2F&h=09d4ced1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201013/K3CF4DXSARC67GJY6D5X7UXCUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n擾秩序案 警直認夾證供 <br />\n同意「&times;你老母」罵警不犯法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JNSEB6X7mG4YV1ne2fY0y8HIKTI=/3150x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4FRIEGMXSRBDLNPHVNGQGBK5GQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJNSEB6X7mG4YV1ne2fY0y8HIKTI%3D%2F3150x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4FRIEGMXSRBDLNPHVNGQGBK5GQ.jpg&h=947ea7c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員林華彬承認庭上供詞是與同僚事後「夾出嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。。。庭上片段顯示其中一名被告在沒反抗下，遭警員用警棍打至頭破血流兼被噴胡椒噴霧。負責拘捕的警員昨出庭作供時，被發現庭上證供與書面有關時間的證供有出入，他直認相關資料是其他同僚事後「夾出嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n控方指兩被告。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IxcfT8hq0AuFPk_DK68AmKeXvSc=/2624x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G7CB37D4KNADPMLAQPXXESQQ54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIxcfT8hq0AuFPk_DK68AmKeXvSc%3D%2F2624x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG7CB37D4KNADPMLAQPXXESQQ54.jpg&h=5e0b5639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■兩名被告當晚在元朗遭警員包抄截查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告無反抗 遭棍毆噴椒<br />\n<br />\n負責拘捕被告的防暴警24418林華彬供稱，當晚與原隸屬港島區機動部隊Z連的數十名警員，前往元朗區執行「踏浪者」行動。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播片顯示，多名防暴警突然從一邊行人路衝向對面行人路包抄兩名被告，盧沒有反抗下，警員用警棍將他打至頭破血流，朝面部噴胡椒噴霧。盧大嗌：「我做咗乜嘢呀？」兩被告繼而被推向鐵閘外搜查。及後趙發現盧頭部流血，要求警員給紙巾為盧止血，惟林稱不知盧受傷。對於片段沒拍到有叫囂或擲雜物，林聲稱只是「條片影唔到」。片中有年長街坊不值警員所為理論，說：「以後係𡃁仔嘅世界，做乜要咁對佢。」<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問林，指林沒即時拘捕被告及警誡，林解釋需先向上級報告。辯方問：「唔通喺街見到賊都要先知會上級先拘捕？」林答「可以咁講」。辯方要求林解釋為何他於庭上就警誡被告及帶返警署時間的內容，與口供紙所述不符。林承認是與其他同僚事後「夾出嚟」。裁判官梁雅忻聞言問林「仲有咩時間係夾出嚟」，林稱「太耐唔記得」。林同意，向警察講「&times;你老母」並不犯法。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：TMCC433/20"},{"pid":"0f8095b73efd7e5d5ff417080f0427d0e23324ec","tid":2241214,"uid":49329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"仆街黑警死全家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a678fe2c52e2ec6cb616d44dde667f681d6e2e20","tid":2241214,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"食咗誠實豆沙包"},{"pid":"c63c08b9608fff575441de5c41a7b5bad0c1af99","tid":2241214,"uid":58998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"繼續無後果"},{"pid":"b930697ce51bb3c813a8b355c949a6129ef47489","tid":2241214,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a678fe2c52e2ec6cb616d44dde667f681d6e2e20","tid":2241214,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"食咗誠實豆沙包"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"智力低到連大話都唔識字講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}